      <subsection name="Examples" id="EmptyLineWrappingInBlock_Examples">
        <p id="Example1-config">
          To configure the check with default (only CLASS_DEF, both separators allowed):
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="EmptyLineWrappingInBlock"/&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example1-code">
          Example:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
class Example1 {

  private int field;

}
</code></pre></div><hr class="example-separator"/>
        <p id="Example2-config">
          To configure the check for method bodies: top allows empty line, bottom forbids empty line
          (as in <a href="https://github.com/checkstyle/checkstyle/issues/5313">#5313</a>):
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="EmptyLineWrappingInBlock"&gt;
      &lt;property name="tokens" value="METHOD_DEF"/&gt;
      &lt;property name="topSeparator" value="empty_line_allowed"/&gt;
      &lt;property name="bottomSeparator" value="no_empty_line"/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example2-code">
          Example:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
class Example2 {
  private void doSomething() {
    // method body
  }

  void ok() {
    doSomething();
  }

  void violation() {
    doSomething();

  } // violation 'No empty line is allowed before the closing brace.'
}
</code></pre></div><hr class="example-separator"/>
        <p id="Example3-config">
          To require exactly one empty line after opening brace and before closing brace
          for classes:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-xml">
&lt;module name="Checker"&gt;
  &lt;module name="TreeWalker"&gt;
    &lt;module name="EmptyLineWrappingInBlock"&gt;
      &lt;property name="tokens" value="CLASS_DEF"/&gt;
      &lt;property name="topSeparator" value="empty_line"/&gt;
      &lt;property name="bottomSeparator" value="empty_line"/&gt;
    &lt;/module&gt;
  &lt;/module&gt;
&lt;/module&gt;
</code></pre></div>
        <p id="Example3-code">
          Example:
        </p>
        <div class="wrapper"><pre class="prettyprint"><code class="language-java">
// violation above 'Exactly one empty line is required after the opening brace.'
class Example3 {
  private int x;
} // violation 'Exactly one empty line is required before the closing brace.'

class Ok {

  private int x;

}
</code></pre></div>
      </subsection>

